&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener nofollow noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.routledge.com&#x2F;Routledge-Frequency-Dictionaries&#x2F;book-series&#x2F;RFD&quot;&gt;频率词典&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener nofollow noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.reddit.com&#x2F;r&#x2F;language_exchange&#x2F;comments&#x2F;dcaeq2&#x2F;all_websites_for_finding_free_language_courses&#x2F;&quot;&gt;多种免费英语课程资源&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
